{"tid":2119613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港警察藍田墮樓亡 昨涉嫌偷拍裙底被捕","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T12:38:51.000Z","uid":199739,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b596c2c1af80de1106eef0808d2f95879c01ef7c","tid":2119613,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"一名男子今（22日）早8時許，被發現倒臥於德田邨德盛樓平台，懷疑由高處墮下，當場身亡。據了解，死者是一名37歲休班警員，駐守警察總部，主要負責內勤工作，他昨晚涉嫌偷拍裙底被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，事主昨（21日）晚9時許休班時，在藍田啟田商場扶手電梯懷疑偷拍裙底被當場揭發，警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌偷拍將他拘捕，至凌晨時分獲准保釋，惟事主今早8時許被發現在居住的田邨德盛墮樓身亡。消息指，墮樓警員本身患有肌肉疾病及早期柏金遜症，去年曾請2個月大假，疑受病患影響，近月情緒落低，同事得悉其墮樓均感婉惜。<br />\n<br />\nSource: HK01<br />\n<br />\n改正返標題"},{"pid":"84f66df8982ad9c0ccaac6a1375e5e2d81759a66","tid":2119613,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"嗯 好事"},{"pid":"258e12dd256026ebd3f93417732824f37c748b17","tid":2119613,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"(以正視聽) 偷拍裙底之後跳樓果位阿SIR好可能係俾自己人老屈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2119594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2119594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0c0a551ca08f7f57f54df91f6548523f3c33ac86","tid":2119613,"uid":146203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:00:29.000Z","msg":"呢d就真係無可疑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3089ee0a6ff3e5ac268f1da8306c8a5e47eec4b","tid":2119613,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"抵撚死, 死得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb6e54bea861743fe54ada6701590258b282562","tid":2119613,"uid":298225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:13:54.000Z","